    "The motivation for this study was to systematically find, analyze, and synthesize all research articles related to securing federated learning.",
    "Therefore, the SLR was conducted by following Kitchenham's methodology Kitchenham et al. (2009).",
    "Fig. 1 presents the overall structure of our literature review.",
    "The objective of this study is to provide a systematic literature on existing research on the development of neural network-based IDS in the context of Federated Learning. 2.",
